## High-level description
The code defines an interface `OutboundPatientDiscoveryResp` that represents the structure of a response for outbound patient discovery in a healthcare context. This interface extends the `BaseDomainCreate` interface and includes properties from `OutboundPatientDiscoveryRespTableEntry`.
